last_episode_to_air.name: The Horned Dinosaur Mysteries
last_episode_to_air.overview: In northern Alberta scientist try to figure out what killed an entire herd of dinosaurs in one blow. In southern Alberta another team of paleontologists search for the skull bones of what may be a brand new species of horned dinosaurs.

name: Dino Hunt Canada
overview: Documentary narrated by Dan Akroyd of paleontologists searching for dinosaurs and the evidence they left behind.
